snippet.title: The Star Named EOS - Official Trailer | Wholesome Direct 2023
snippet.description:
Check out the latest trailer for The Star Named EOS for another look at the upcoming first-person narrative puzzle game about photography and the ways we can capture the fleeting moments that shape our lives. Check it out to see gameplay like puzzle solving and more. The Star Named EOS will be available on PC.

#GameTrailers #SoG #Gaming
